text: "All Night" is a 2016 song by Beyoncé. It was taken from her sixth studio album Lemonade. It went to number 38 in the United States, number 73 in Canada, number 30 in Hungary, number 60 in the United Kingdom and number 57 in Scotland. ==References== Category:2016 songs Category:Reggae songs Category:R&B; songs Category:Beyoncé songs
title: All Night (Beyoncé song)
